node.text:
How do we #StopTheSame and create real change? 

Gen Z will feel the full force of climate change and they want something to be done about it. 

The Global Youth Biodiversity Network (@gybn_cbd) works with 280 global youth organisations to get the views of its 664,000 young activists in front of business and political decision-makers. 

In its new campaign, #StopTheSame it asks leaders how to they would create change. 

Tap the link in our bio to find out what part Alan Jope thinks sustainable business can do to #StopTheSame losses in the world’s biodiversity .
